  "texts": [
    "The low frequency of misclassifications attests to the resilience and accuracy of the proposed intelligent waste classification model in dealing with a wide range of waste materials.",
    "Moreover, the results point to the possibility of using the proposed waste classification model in real-world settings to manage waste materials and advance sustainable development.",
    "Another experiment is conducted to evaluate the performance of the proposed intelligent waste classification, where the receiver operating characteristic (ROC) curve is utilized.",
    "This curve is frequently applied to compare the true positive rate to the false positive rate and assess how well a classification model is working.",
    "Figure 10 shows that the proposed model's accurate classification rate is significantly greater than its misclassification rate."
  ]
}